                        <h1>Security</h1>
                        <ul>
                            <li>7bit or 8bit encoding of attachments</li>
                            <li>Anti phishing URL check</li>
                            <li>Full GnuPG support</li>
                            <li>On the fly changing of the type of GnupG encryption and/or signing used</li>
                            <li>SSL certificate management</li>
                            <li>(MIME/ascii) in the compose window</li>
                            <li>Manual selection of MIME type and encoding for attachments</li>
                            <li>POP before SMTP authentication</li>
                            <li>Built in GDB crash handler</li>
                            <li>IMAP over SSH tunnel</li>
                            <li>IMAP capability support</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
