                        <h1>Compose</h1>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Reply-finder</li>
                            <li>Spell checking with aspell</li>
                            <li>Drag n drop support</li>
                            <li>Automatic saving of message when composing</li>
                            <li>Face and xface headers support</li>
                            <li>(MIME/ascii) in the compose window</li>
                            <li>Save all attachments in a mail at once</li>
                            <li>Save 2 or more selected files to a single file</li>
                            <li>Reply to part of an email</li>
                        </ul>

                        <h3>Address Book</h3>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Import from LDIF, Mutt, Pine natively</li>
                            <li>Import others via scripts</li>
                            <li>Auto completion of recipients</li>
                            <li>Harvest addresses</li> 
                            <li>Export to various formats</li>
                            <li>User defineable newsgroup names abbreviation length</li>
